{"type": "article", "id": 4052, "title": "Monde Riant 便利贴", "description": "", "date": "2014-12-03T07:31:35Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 10, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233319ubo8R5JIxrApjsLk.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>还记得巴黎设计工作室 Pa Design 曾设计过一款充满想象力的手表便利贴吗？近日，Pa Design 工作室的两位设计师 Assia Quétin 与 Catherine Denoyelle 又带来了一款独特的便利贴设计，名为「Monde Riant」。两人借鉴了荷兰绘画大师彼埃·蒙德里安（Piet Mondrian）的几何形体概念，模仿蒙德里安画室对于线条与色块的运用，将不同的便利贴用不同的颜色与尺寸加以区分，共同贴在一块黑色的底座上，就像蒙德里安的绘画就仍然给人一种三维空间的视觉。定价 13.70 欧元，<a href=\"http://www.pa-design.com/fr/papeterie/347-monde-riant-3575780001785.html?search_query=monde+rian&amp;results=1\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。<br>\r\n<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233317lWI5oaXQMRu4i9vA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052333171Vk9i6TwAvlosPUI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.728125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233318duzO02cFmox5CLSp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.584375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233318Wy0VTXIhaPsLQxKE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br></p>\n\n"}